## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="79c83-109">下列程式碼範例示範如何建立 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> 類別的新執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79c83-109">The following code example demonstrates how to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> class.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="79c83-110">範例程式碼也建立 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeCondition> 和 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup> 類別的新執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79c83-110">The example code also creates new instances of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeCondition> and <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup> classes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79c83-111">這個程式碼範例是 SimpleCAGWorkflow.designer.cs 檔案中＜ConditionedActivityGroup SDK＞範例的一部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79c83-111">This code example is part of the ConditionedActivityGroup SDK sample from the SimpleCAGWorkflow.designer.cs file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79c83-112">如需詳細資訊，請參閱[使用 ConditionedActivityGroup](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5a0b7e9e-def5-46b2-acbb-0005e1aff984)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79c83-112">For more information, see [Using ConditionedActivityGroup](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5a0b7e9e-def5-46b2-acbb-0005e1aff984).</span></span>  

```csharp  
private ConditionedActivityGroup BookingCAG;  
private CodeActivity Car;  
private CodeActivity Airline;  

this.CanModifyActivities = true;  
CodeCondition codecondition1 = new CodeCondition();  
CodeCondition codecondition2 = new CodeCondition();  
this.BookingCAG = new ConditionedActivityGroup();  
this.Car = new CodeActivity();  
this.Airline = new CodeActivity();  
```
